    <h1>Multi-environment AWS, from a <span class="accent">single codebase</span></h1>
    <p class="sub">Provision and configure dev, staging, and prod environments of different sizes using Terraform workspaces and reusable modules — then let Ansible configure every server in parallel. Remote state with locking, secrets in AWS Secrets Manager, and zero static credentials.</p>

