    <h2>One codebase, three sizes</h2>
    <p class="lead">The workspace you select drives a counts map in <span class="mono">main.tf</span>. Same modules, same code — only the numbers change.</p>
    <div class="grid3">
      <div class="envcard dev">
        <div class="name"><span class="led"></span> dev</div>
        <div class="res">
          <div><span class="v">2</span><span class="k">EC2</span></div>
